metadata.name: Ginseng Hercules
metadata.description:
The holders of the two hundred fifty (250) Ginseng Hercules tokens will be invited to join twelve (12) Mindset Mentoring Sessions with an International Coaching Federation Certified Coach per "year" (i.e.). Each year shall be defined as the twelve months time period commencing Apr 24, 2022, Apr 24, 2023, and Apr 24, 2024. After Apr 24, 2024, the services and utilities offered will be updated in order to remain aligned with our vision

In other words, there are thirty-six (36) total redemptions occurring as follows: - Twelve (12) redemptions must occur between Apr 24, 2022, and Apr 24, 2023 - Twelve (12) redemptions must occur between Apr 24, 2023, and Apr 24, 2024 - Twelve (12) redemptions must occur between Apr 24, 2024, and Apr 24, 2025

All-access experiences will be pre-scheduled in advance with 15 days' notice via a Ginseng Effect representative

This token is eligible to obtain additional perks as specified on the official [Ginseng Effect Academy website](https://academy.ginsengeffect.com/) 

This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain
